Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:09.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:19.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:39.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:46.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:53.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:59.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:06.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:14.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:20.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:28.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:31.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:32.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:36.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Para-sama's pair! You can't\Njust tell me to team up with Alty now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:41.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is all for the sake of restoring\NChor Tempest to its former prestige.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:46.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:47.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why aren't their prayers\Nbeing heard by the Simoun gem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:52.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:53.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:57.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that!\NI said stop calling me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:02:03.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Reason
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their prayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:27.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, the divine vehicles are\Nactivated by Simoun sibylla prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:32.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,The two priestesses are joined in\Nspirit as they honor Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:40.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,To reject the one you're paired with\Nis the same as rejecting the Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:48.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I really find that hard to believe.\NWe've never heard such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:53.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm only speculating.\NEven so, thanks to your efforts...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:57.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we were able to discover\Na secret aspect of the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well done...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:02.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,...or would that be\Ninappropriate to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:04.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,What this means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:10.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is that my sister and I won't be\Nable to fly as a pair anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:15.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you think you\Ncan understand why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:16.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,No enemies in sight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:36.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so bored to death it feels\Nlike I'm gonna get moldy all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:37.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nyou'd rather we were at war?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:46.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never said that.\NIt's just that there's nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:51.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Such sinful thoughts should be\Nbanished from your mind right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:56.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so bored! I'm so bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:07.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,She doesn't look it, but Roatreamon\Ncan be scary when she gets mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:22.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Something that's not on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:27.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:31.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, the ultimate Ri Majon\Nthat can be achieved by a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,They say it can inscribe\Nthe final miracle on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:35.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Final?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:41.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simulating the Emerald\NRi Majon of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:45.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,How would that make\NNeviril feel if she saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was I doing a Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:50.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:53.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that's what that was all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:56.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer.\NHey, tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:02.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,\NI've never seen it before myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:05.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Waporif, didn't Neviril and Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:19.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,So Neviril and Amuria did it.\NThe Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:24.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,I get it! They didn't succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:31.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that's it. Not with Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:51.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh my! You're so thorough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:54.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,The god\NTempus Spatium is a neat freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:58.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,If the water's murky,\NTempus Spatium won't come near.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:00.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what Mother said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:04.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,According to her, misfortune seeps in\Nthrough dirty kitchens and bathtubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:08.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're amazing. You know so\Nmany things I've never heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe it best suits me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:14.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Cleaning house\Nlike this, cooking meals...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:19.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was only\Ndreaming for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:23.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's so stuck on I can barely\Nscrape it off! If we had citrus...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:24.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Citrus?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,The acid rubs stains away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:29.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,As I said, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:05.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:09.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do it with me! The Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:20.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know.\NIt was a bust with Amuria, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know I'll work out. Come on,\NNeviril, let's do the Emerald...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:27.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:37.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:40.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll get something to wipe that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:46.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:49.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,We just don't talk about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because it reminds\Nyou of Amuria's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:06.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was just going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I feel so sorry for Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never knew Amuria personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:28.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,But to speak ill of\Nthe dead is an unforgivable sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:31.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on. I was only...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:32.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:38.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why'd you bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:58.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Jeez.\NListen, do you love Neviril or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:01.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then how?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:08.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wishing to chat just a second more\Nor hold her tight and feel her warmth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:12.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,The kind of love where you\Ndesire her more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,I desire Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:18.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I'm with Neviril,\NI know I can fly higher than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:21.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,How'd it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:32.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since we're not about\Nto go into battle, it felt weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:38.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,When you stop feeling that way,\Nit'll mean you're really in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:42.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril was in love with Amuria.\NDo you get what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:45.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do\Nwith the Emerald Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:50.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's better in all kinds\Nof ways when you're in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:56.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:00.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It'll happen with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:44.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because it reminds\Nyou of Amuria's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:01.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! What's wrong, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:05.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:43.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll open the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:48.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's horribly dusty in here, but Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:51.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,You'd rather not be in the same\Nroom with everybody, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:59.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right... you get some rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:25.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:29.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,It must be incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:33.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like to try it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:35.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,With Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:39.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't really mind who I do it with...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you love Dominüra, Rimone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:51.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you do, then you'll want to kiss even\Nwhen you're not in a Simoun, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:55.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hear it's better in all\Nways when you're in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:56.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,All kinds?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, all kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did the Powers That Be say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:17.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,That so long as the enemy's idle,\Nwe'll take a wait-and-see approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:20.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,After discovering that aerial base,\Nthey're saying to let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:24.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems an unexpected crisis\Noccurred aboard the Arcus Prima...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and everything's in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:28.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:32.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the here and now is so distracting\Nthat they're missing the big picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,If this goes on, Kyuukoku will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:37.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:41.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I may, you seem\Nto be in some kind of rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:45.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Far be it from me to presume\Nsuch things of a sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:48.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I would say that's accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:00.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:04.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NIs there some problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:06.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:15.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you feel like you were in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Run along now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:44.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria is... dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:52.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:56.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whoops-a-daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:16.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Look at me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:22.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,You could choke in this room.\NIt's full of old junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no air circulation.\NAll that's left...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:28.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is useless memories, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:39.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've got to go.\NLet's open the door together, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,T-That hurts, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:11.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril's exhausted. Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I said get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:31.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, I don't think Aer\Nmeans you any harm. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:35.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to get some sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:40.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where's Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:06.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:10.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,What she said was\Nshocking, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not just Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:17.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,All this time, the rest\Nof us were avoiding it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Saying those words out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:24.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because if we did, it felt as though\Nwe'd never be able to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:28.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria was so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:33.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Always looking skyward...\NShe never seemed unsure of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:38.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, war was something\NI never thought I could handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:43.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but if she was there,\NI thought we couldn't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:45.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's how she made me feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:49.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I was afraid to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:53.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I still don't want\Nto admit it, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:54.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:04.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:08.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Uh, guess I'm busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:10.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:15.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:23.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's awful!\NWhat kind of animal is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:26.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,So funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!\NI worked really hard sewing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:31.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure, I made him a little uglier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:34.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's already met his doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:37.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, he hasn't. He's so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:41.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess you could\Nsay he took after his creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:42.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:03.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never wanted to hurt Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:08.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just that I felt if we were together,\Nwe could accomplish anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can you be so sure of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:16.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you never\Nexperienced utter despair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:21.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I had, what good would it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:30.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Entrusting Neviril to you\Nmay have been a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:43.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to wait\Nfor orders from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:48.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now that the enemy's idle,\Nwe must investigate that aerial base.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:51.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, Aer, I leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, these two are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:57.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those two are, at the moment,\NChor Tempest's top pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is the issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:00.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:06.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra, I'm not in a place\Nwhere I can team up with Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:09.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said so\Nyesterday, right? The Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:11.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's precisely why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:16.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,People's emotions aren't toys!\NIf you're speculating...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:17.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I... want to fly with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:27.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe you don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:36.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want you to put\NKyuukoku above all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:40.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are Simoun sibyllae after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:20.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I knew it was futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:22.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I knew it was futile.\NIt's not futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:26.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not futile.\NYou and I will be able to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:27.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:45.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their prayers were heard, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,So emotional stuff had\Nnothing to do with it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:53.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not possible. The only\Nexplanation would be that Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:11.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I knew it. You're seeking me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:19.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can fly if you're with me.\NYou can do it if you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:22.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Am I really seeking Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:25.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Surely not...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:28.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I... Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:34.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I'm afraid of Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.05,0:22:47.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.79,0:22:51.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:58.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.07,0:23:06.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:19.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:24.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:28.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:32.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.71,0:23:38.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.65,0:23:44.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.12,0:23:47.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.59,0:23:53.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:59.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:05.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.51,0:24:11.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to dismantle\Na Simoun, Sibylla Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.11,0:24:15.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.25,0:24:16.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sacrosanct\NNext time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:18.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sacrosanct\NSacrosanct.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.59,0:24:19.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sacrosanct
